    "hypothesis": "稳健版EfficiencyScarcity。衡量‘买压转换率’的非线性突变。如果单位买压产生的梯度(gradient/flux)在极短时间内骤降至中期均值的30%以下，说明市场进入了严重的非对称受阻状态。",
    "code": "def sig(cs1h, cs4h=None):\n    if not cs1h or not cs4h or len(cs1h) < 12 or len(cs4h) < 6:\n        return None\n    \n    # 定义转换率：梯度 / (买压-0.45) 修正偏移量以放大波动感应\n    def get_conversion(cs, n):\n        f = flux(cs, n)\n        return gradient(cs, n) / (f - 0.4 if f > 0.4 else 0.05)\n\n    conv_short = get_conversion(cs1h, 2)\n    conv_long = get_conversion(cs1h, 10)\n    \n    # 4h看跌，1h在反弹中转换率发生断崖式下跌，且flux跌破中性\n    if gradient(cs4h, 6) < -0.005 and gradient(cs1h, 3) > 0.001:\n        if conv_short < conv_long * 0.25 and flux(cs1h, 2) < 0.49:\n            return \"SHORT\"\n    return None",
