    "name": "FrictionDecouplingShort",
    "mode": "mtf_self",
    "hypothesis": "修正FrictionEfficiency。通过观察‘K线实体占比’与‘买压flux’的背离：如果买压维持在中性以上但K线实体却迅速收缩，说明内部摩擦力（阻力）已达到临界点。",
    "code": "def sig(cs1h, cs4h=None):\n    if not cs1h or not cs4h or len(cs1h) < 10 or len(cs4h) < 6:\n        return None\n    \n    # 计算K线实体占比\n    body_ratio = (abs(cs1h[-1][\"close\"] - cs1h[-1][\"open\"])) / (cs1h[-1][\"high\"] - cs1h[-1][\"low\"] + 1e-9)\n    \n    # 逻辑：4h下行背景，1h反弹。如果Flux仍然>0.48（多头还在努力），但实体占比跌破0.25，\n    # 说明多头的努力绝大部分被空头头寸抵消，上涨动力已经枯竭。\n    if gradient(cs4h, 6) < -0.004 and gradient(cs1h, 3) > 0.001:\n        if flux(cs1h, 2) > 0.48 and body_ratio < 0.25:\n            if flux(cs1h, 1) < flux(cs1h, 3): # 买压开始边际减弱\n                return \"SHORT\"\n    return None",
